  "instructions": [
    "heat the olive oil in a large pot over medium heat",
    "add the onion and sauté until softened",
    "add the garlic and sauté for 1 minute",
    "add the smoked paprika and dried chillies and sauté for 1 minute",
    "add the lentils, vegetable broth, bay leaves, caraway seeds and red wine vinegar",
    "bring to the boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes",
    "season with salt and pepper to taste",
    "serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley",
    "serve with rye bread or over mashed potatoes"
